text: Frank Zappa for President is a compilation album by American musician Frank Zappa, released in July 2016, consisting of unreleased compositions played on the Synclavier and unheard tracks relating to the uniting political thread that ties it all together. ==Track listing== == Personnel == *All titles performed/arranged/conducted by Frank Zappa == References == Category:Frank Zappa albums Category:2015 albums Category:Albums published posthumously
title: Frank Zappa for President
